<title>JAPAN: DKB says to take steps to prevent more scandals.</title>
<headline>DKB says to take steps to prevent more scandals.</headline>
<dateline>TOKYO 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Dai-Ichi Kangyo Bank Ltd said on Friday it would work out steps to prevent a recurrence of a scandal in which it has been linked to a &quot;sokaiya&quot; corporate racketeer.</p>
</text>
